The paper proposes a new method for regularization in neural network training, which is a common topic in machine learning and specifically in the subfield of deep learning. The paper also discusses the application of the proposed method to network compression, which is another common topic in deep learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
